# Astro Diffusion

Fine-tune SD1.5 on astronomy images, evaluate, and demo a base vs fine-tuned UI.

## Quickstart

```bash
# 1) Install
pip install -r requirements.txt

# 2) Prepare data
# produce data/train.jsonl and data/val.jsonl with {"path","caption"} lines

# 3) Train (LoRA)
accelerate launch src/training.py --config configs/train_sd15.yaml

# 4) Update configs/infer.yaml -> model_dir: outputs/sd15_sft/checkpoint-best

# 5) Run UI
python src/ui_gradio.py --config configs/infer.yaml
